name: Space King
description:
Bienvenido a "Space King", una colección de NFTs que te lleva en un viaje cósmico a través de reinos estelares y galaxias desconocidas. Cada pieza en esta serie representa un fragmento del vasto universo, fusionando arte digital con conceptos astronómicos para crear un espectáculo visual único. Desde planetas distantes y nebulosas vibrantes hasta reyes cósmicos que gobiernan galaxias lejanas, "Space King" explora la majestuosidad del cosmos a través de una lente creativa y audaz.

Esta colección es para visionarios, soñadores y amantes del espacio, ofreciendo una visión artística del infinito. Cada NFT no solo es una obra de arte, sino también un portal a un universo donde la imaginación y la realidad se encuentran en la frontera final. Sumérgete en "Space King" y reclama tu trono en el cosmos.

name: Emotional Fantasia by Noriko
description: Welcome to the world of Emotional Fantasia, where emotions come alive in vibrant hues and abstract forms. Explore a kaleidoscope of feelings through our collection of abstract art pieces, each intricately crafted to capture the depth and complexity of human emotion. From the serenity of tranquil blues to the fiery passion of bold reds, every artwork in Emotional Fantasia invites you on a journey through the rich tapestry of the human experience. Immerse yourself in this whimsical realm where imagination knows no bounds and emotions dance freely on the canvas.

name: Munjado Delights by Boyane
description: 600 years ago, the mighty Joseon Dynasty was formed, ushering in a period of flourishing art and culture on the Korean peninsula. This era saw the birth of Munjado, a unique form of folk painting where strokes of a brush conveyed characters, stories, and identity. Today, French street artist Boyane Zelechowski (AKA BOYANE) pays homage to this rich heritage with "Munjado Delights," a collection of 3 NFTs that reinterpret this ancient Asian tradition with savvy European finesse. Like pieces of a puzzle, each NFT is assembled and reassembled with rich imagery and meaning that coincide with one another- telling a new story in an ancient fashion.

name: Urban Eyes 3D
description: Introducing "Urban Eyes 3D,” a dynamic collection of 3D NFTs inspired by street art, graffiti, and the works of prominent street artists from Brazil and around the world. Each NFT in this vibrant collection features a unique eye motif, meticulously crafted with vibrant colors and captivating 3D visuals. Drawing influence from the bustling streets of Brazil and urban landscapes worldwide, "Urban Eyes 3D” captures the essence of street culture in stunning detail. With its fusion of street art aesthetics and cutting-edge 3D design, this collection offers an immersive experience that celebrates urban creativity and global influence.

description: The Glorious Founding Membership (GFM) is designed to recognise those early supporters of the Glorious vision. It is a community of like-minded culture, sport and art lovers who are journeying with us into this new frontier of digital ownership. Along the way, your membership allows for gifts of digital art that can be displayed on your Samsung Frame along with exclusive access and experiences.
